casebody.data:
In re C.D.A.W., a Minor Child.
appealed by Respondent Mother. No. 110A06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 16, 2006. Gary C. Rhodes, Salisbury, for Angela Wright Eagle. James A. Dickens, Assistant Guilford County Attorney, for Guilford County DSS. Joyce Terres, Attorney Advocate, for Guardian ad Litem. Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 625 S.E.2d 139 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 16th day of March 2006 by Guilford County Department of Social Services in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th day of November 2006."
